request.description:
For /employees endpoint there is a list of special filter parameters:

<p><b>Workarea id filter</b></p>

filter[workarea_id]={workarea_id} 

This filter parameter can be used for filter employees by workarea id

<p><b>Tags included filter</b></p>

filter[tags_included]={tag_id1,tag_idN}

This filter parameter can be used for filter employees by included tags

<p><b>Tags excluded filter</b></p>

filter[tags_excluded]={tag_id1,tag_idN}

This filter parameter can be used for filter employees by excluded tags

<p><b>Service id filter</b></p>

filter[service_id]={service_id}

This filter parameter can be used fo filter employees by service id

